resources.string: Lolu hlelo lokusebenza luhunyushwe yi-Google Humusha. IsiNgisi ulimi lwangempela lwalolu hlelo lokusebenza. Uyacelwa ukuthi ukhumbule ukuthi kungahle kube namaphutha athile ekuhumusheni.
Uma ufuna ukushintsha ulimi lwe-app libe isiNgisi ungakwenza lokho kuzilungiselelo.
Sicela usisekele ngokulinganisa lolu hlelo lokusebenza. Ngiyabonga!
